                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "C'est jour de paye, et, par groupes de quatre ou cinq,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6−6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Les ouvriers, malgré leurs mines échinées,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Entrent en ricanant pour s'offrir des tournées.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Dans une heure d'ici, de l'assommoir flambant",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Ils sortiront, les yeux fixes, en titubant.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Qu'y faire ? Ce poison seulement les console.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Dehors, des femmes vont, nu-tête, en camisole,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Et des enfants portant des pains aussi gros qu'eux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Dans ce quartier sinistre où le regard du gueux",
