                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Dans tous ces cœurs aigris, la révolte macère",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Contre ce Dieu qui veut qu'on aime sa misère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Et, l'accusant de la cruauté de leur sort,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6−6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Ils le repoussent même à l'heure de la mort.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
